Package org.oa4mp.delegation.common.token

Interface Token

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Serializable
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    AccessToken, AuthorizationGrant, NewToken, RefreshToken, Verifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AccessTokenImpl, AuthorizationGrantImpl, IDTokenImpl, OA1AccessTokenImpl, OA1AuthorizationGrantImpl, OA1TokenImpl, RefreshTokenImpl, TokenImpl, VerifierImpl
    public interface Token
extends Serializable
    General top-level object for tokens in a delegation system. All token are derivative of this. Differing implementations may have to extend this.
